Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.20,0:00:20.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.41,0:00:22.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.87,0:00:29.96,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.89,0:00:40.51,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.51,0:00:43.98,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.98,0:00:49.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.52,0:00:55.74,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:01:02.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.75,0:01:07.25,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.25,0:01:09.34,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:16.51,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.22,0:01:26.64,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.64,0:01:30.23,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.23,0:01:35.78,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:41.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, let's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.99,0:01:48.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.71,0:01:53.17,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:55.17,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.67,0:02:00.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:03.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:04.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.52,0:02:06.23,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:07.89,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:09.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:11.06,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.06,0:02:12.98,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:14.40,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.40,0:02:15.61,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.61,0:02:19.91,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:22.20,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:26.54,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.54,0:02:29.00,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:33.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:35.42,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:39.51,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:42.72,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.68,0:02:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:02:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.90,0:02:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.98,0:02:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.32,0:03:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.87,0:03:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.49,0:03:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.37,0:03:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the thing about phoenixes:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.06,0:03:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter the hardship,\Nthey always rise back up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they're reborn even stronger than before!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.98,0:03:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.65,0:03:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, men! I was a foolish\Ncaptain who couldn't live up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to the trust my precious friend placed in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.24,0:03:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... But I wanna let...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Vigaro see it once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.33,0:03:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has to see our flag flying\Nabove the ocean where he's at rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Give back my flag!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.76,0:04:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like Luffy is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.14,0:04:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's come for our Jolly Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.89,0:04:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! We're finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.64,0:04:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! We can still make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. I don't know how\NLuffy learned about the flag,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's not as though he\Nwitnessed it getting stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.48,0:04:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep! Which means we've still got a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.90,0:04:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know where the Jolly Roger is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.57,0:04:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.16,0:04:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're far more reliable\Nthan that lame moss head.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.96,0:04:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise to become my big sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.92,0:04:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do and I'll save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've made a fool of the Accino Family!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the one who stole\Nour Jolly Roger, Naked Balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.69,0:05:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph! So what if I did, whippersnapper?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna kick your butt right\Nquick and get our flag back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.20,0:05:18.17,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"The Super Hot-Hot Final Battle!\NLuffy vs. the Scorching Hot Don"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.13,0:05:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! So you're a Devil\NFruit power holder, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It truly has been a long time\Nsince I personally hunted a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be honored, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.52,0:05:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don Accino...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.27,0:05:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he's the head of that\Nfamily of bounty hunters, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.61,0:05:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What type of powers did he\Nget from the Hot-Hot Fruit...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.98,0:05:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's his fault that the temperature\Nhas been going up and down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.91,0:05:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to kick my butt?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.57,0:05:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking back, I've met countless\Npirates who've made that same claim.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.08,0:05:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what happened to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.87,0:06:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Each and every one...\N--Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.58,0:06:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should let me finish talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.21,0:06:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot! Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.64,0:06:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can melt... anything I touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.36,0:06:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.61,0:06:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still think you can win?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.03,0:06:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Battle Axe!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It burns!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.08,0:06:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy's attacks aren't working!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't even touched the guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.17,0:06:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.38,0:06:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still don't get it, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.18,0:06:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--He's hot! Hot! Hot! Hot!\N--Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.22,0:07:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't lay so much as a finger on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.31,0:07:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's too hot to punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.40,0:07:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lookie! Slip, slip, slip away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.11,0:07:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.62,0:07:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can even do stuff like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.79,0:07:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My entire body is suspended\Nby the tiny bit of steam
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.25,0:07:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,emitted from the ice melted\Nby the soles of my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome! That's so neat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.14,0:07:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Slippity-slip!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.23,0:07:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Slip around like fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.61,0:07:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh heh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wahoo!\N--Screech!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.50,0:08:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Hot-Hot ability isn't all that bad after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what I should have expected\Nfrom a 300-million Berry bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.79,0:08:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good at what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.51,0:08:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.51,0:08:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the real fight has just begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot Makeup!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see a thing! What's he up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot-Fried Tofu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.98,0:08:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our flags are somewhere inside that house...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.36,0:08:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jiro, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.07,0:08:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.70,0:08:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.41,0:08:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.54,0:08:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.12,0:08:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.96,0:08:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love children.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.34,0:08:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.38,0:08:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I only love my children!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.88,0:08:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That burns!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.97,0:08:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.93,0:09:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Naked Balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.27,0:09:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't throw a hissy fit. I'll play with you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.52,0:09:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.19,0:09:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready for the finishing move?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Steam...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.53,0:09:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Iron!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.61,0:09:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! We can't afford to let\NPapa's temper grow any hotter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.04,0:09:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa is going to claim\NStraw Hat's head, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.92,0:09:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least, I need to\Ntake out this 100-Berry-bounty,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.96,0:09:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I can lift his spirits\Nback up as much as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I can't hand my head\Nover to a lowly bounty hunter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.98,0:09:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Puzzle, you may think you're\Nfighting on par with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.07,0:09:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the tables are about to turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm frozen to the bone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.50,0:10:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.29,0:10:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men, is this the best the\NPhoenix Pirates can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.72,0:10:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, it's about time I took your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.69,0:10:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.15,0:10:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You didn't take any damage?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.65,0:10:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was burning hot at first, but luckily\Nthe ice cooled me right off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.82,0:10:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right? This time I'll melt\Nyour entire body in a flash...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.33,0:10:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I don't have to endure any\Nmore of your insolent garbage!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.83,0:10:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heat Level Up: 3,000 Degrees!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's an impressive amount of smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.30,0:10:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.92,0:10:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't touch you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.23,0:11:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.86,0:11:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Bazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! He went flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.41,0:11:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.49,0:11:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time to be rejoicing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.50,0:11:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, Luffy will go after\Nthe Jolly Roger in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.04,0:11:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! Crap! He'll find out that\Nthey stole our flag for real!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.26,0:11:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's holding Robin up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Curse you, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.65,0:12:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as you lose the ability to manipulate\Nthat vexing chain, you're finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These penguins plan on freezing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.03,0:12:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then they'll come in for\Nthe kill once we can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.37,0:12:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Damn it!\N--The beasts!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.25,0:12:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men, fall into a close formation\Nso we can share body heat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.76,0:12:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is so wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm working up a nasty sweat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.64,0:12:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moron! It's not like I want to do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.43,0:12:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men, do you feel nice and warm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather fight than keep this up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm with him, Commander Stansen!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.86,0:12:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the spirit! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.62,0:12:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Puzzle, prepare to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.91,0:12:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one going down!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.46,0:13:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is our flag?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.18,0:13:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.77,0:13:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the first man to ever bring me\Nto my hands and knees, Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? You've still got some fight left in you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.36,0:13:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're also the first\Nto have truly made me mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.82,0:13:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heat Level Up: 5,500 Degrees!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.91,0:13:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot Omelet Shots!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.08,0:13:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don Accino...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.83,0:13:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-chan still hasn't given the sign,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.58,0:13:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which means we're stuck\Nreclaiming the flag ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.59,0:13:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure does! We've gotta beat Luffy to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep an eye on Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.47,0:13:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it for our strategy meeting!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.68,0:13:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all set!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.85,0:13:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Jiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.05,0:13:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for making you worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.14,0:13:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't worried any!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.89,0:14:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That aside, we've gotta get our flag back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.11,0:14:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! We're going to reclaim our--\Nthe Phoenix Pirates'--pride!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.57,0:14:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Uh-huh!\N--Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.57,0:14:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, it's horrible! Our ship pulled\Naway from the shore all on its own!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.91,0:14:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave the ship to us!\NCaptain, you go with Jiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.96,0:14:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, Stansen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Jiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.96,0:14:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're one slippery brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.52,0:14:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're done for, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.39,0:14:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this! Hot-Hot Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.73,0:14:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! That's my move!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.61,0:14:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But your shots are moving\Nat the same speed as earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.66,0:14:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stupid! Hurry and run for it, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.92,0:15:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.05,0:15:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That startled me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.34,0:15:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about your bounty anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to melt you into nothing but steam!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.72,0:15:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't 300-million-Berry\Nsteam sound luxurious?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.06,0:15:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Straw Hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.56,0:15:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a sauna, Naked Balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Evaporate off the face of the planet, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.80,0:15:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot! Hot! Hot! Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That burns!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.26,0:15:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of you, my darling\Ndaughter and sons were...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:15:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.02,0:16:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The temperature keeps climbing up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.23,0:16:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is his Hot-Hot Fruit to blame?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.45,0:16:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There might be more to it than that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.85,0:16:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Sanji, Franky's missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.02,0:16:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the heck did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.69,0:16:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about him!\NI'm sure he has plans of his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.82,0:16:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be the Savage Penguins' doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.90,0:16:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! They trashed our raiding dory,\Nso we can't go after them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:17:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they retaliating for how\Nwe took out their friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.58,0:17:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how messed up are these penguins?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The captain and Jiro will\Ndefinitely get our Jolly Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.79,0:17:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't bear to face them if they came back
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.80,0:17:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and there wasn't a ship\Non which to hoist the flag!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.26,0:17:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander Stansen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.48,0:17:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Big Sister Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay here with me forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.57,0:17:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise that you won't go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.24,0:17:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that, Lil.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.58,0:17:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.50,0:17:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Robin-chan!\N--Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you do as I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.38,0:17:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that kid controlling the plant?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.76,0:17:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll give her a good spanking!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.67,0:17:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are strictly prohibited from\Nraising your hand against a lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.59,0:18:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a broad definition of the term...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.10,0:18:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unhand Robin-chan, you stinking flower!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.98,0:18:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you--! Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are your friends all that important to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.86,0:18:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I want to get our flag back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.32,0:18:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hat Crew's flag?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa enjoys collecting a bunch of Jolly Rogers,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.83,0:18:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't care about those scraps of cloth...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.79,0:18:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, they may be nothing\Nmore than scraps of cloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.71,0:18:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But to us pirates, our flag is\Nmore important than life itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.59,0:18:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's something we can't lose, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.69,0:18:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they really all that important...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.61,0:18:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! Papa...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.15,0:18:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's really angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.24,0:19:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-S-Save--!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.99,0:19:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only saying this for your own good!\NYou'll get indigestion if you eat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.96,0:19:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Lil!\N--Special Attack! Exploding Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.55,0:19:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lil!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.27,0:19:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.73,0:19:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sister Robin...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.90,0:19:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If anything were to happen to you,\Nyour big sister and brothers would be sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.61,0:19:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're their cute, precious little sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.49,0:19:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold your family dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.01,0:20:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we on top of a...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.76,0:20:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second... Gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.26,0:20:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to the New World?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.22,0:20:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. After I get our Jolly Roger back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.27,0:20:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never get there. Your destination\Nwas set in stone a long time ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.65,0:20:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already decided that's where I'm headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.74,0:20:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm definitely going there after I kick your butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.33,0:20:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Jet Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.34,0:20:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.82,0:21:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.03,0:21:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.57,0:21:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.45,0:21:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let go, even if it kills me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.79,0:21:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our pride as pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.83,0:21:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.51,0:21:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Captain... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did great, Jiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.82,0:21:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surprisingly Hot Nose Jet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.57,0:21:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! I... I made sure to get it! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.54,0:21:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we made it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.67,0:22:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it, Nami-san! Now Luffy\Nwon't make fun of--whoa, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.46,0:22:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! What's with that flag?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.85,0:22:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.43,0:22:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd it turn out like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.73,0:22:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like we get to start over from scratch...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.73,0:22:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't Robin, Sanji-kun,\Nand the others make it in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.20,0:22:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope ours isn't amongst those...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.22,0:22:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My beloved family...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.59,0:22:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Lovely Land...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.89,0:22:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now my prized collection!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.85,0:23:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear, I will personally take you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.52,0:23:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot-Hot powers, to the max!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.11,0:23:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maximum Heat Level: 10,000 Degrees!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.53,0:23:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can still heat up?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.29,0:23:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are those two up to?!\NThe ice is melting right and left!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.30,0:23:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like they're going all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.22,0:23:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm starting to get\Nconcerned about our Log Pose.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.51,0:23:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're unbelievable! I guess I'll go\Npick them up in my super ship right quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.10,0:23:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.44,0:23:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"We'll Be Waiting in the New World!\NParting with the Courageous Pirates"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.65,0:23:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
